data.purpose: IIFL FINANCE LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 23-Dec-2024 to consider Fund raising.

Pursuant to the powers delegated by the Board of Directors of the Company, a meeting of the Finance Committee of the Board of Directors of the Company is scheduled to be held on Monday, December 23, 2024 to convert the existing medium term note programme into a global medium term note programme
IIFL FINANCE LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 13-Nov-2024 to consider Fund raising.
IIFL FINANCE LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 31-Oct-2024 to consider Fund raising.

To consider and approve the public issue of secured, rated, listed, redeemable non-convertible debentures, in one or more tranches, in compliance with the provisions of the Securities and Exchange Board of India (Issue and Listing of Non-Convertible Securities) Regulations, 2021, as amended, subject to regulatory and statutory approvals, as may be applicable.
